<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<em><strong>No Spoilers here, please.</strong></em> <p>
A hated and persecuted race of nocturnal dwarves, these cave-dwellers are not  bothered much by darkness. Their natural inclination to magically enchanted  items has made them immune to effects which could drain away magical energy,  and, like ordinary dwarves, they can examine the dungeon to discover traps  and secret doors. 
</p>
<p>
